==Russian==

===Etymology===
For individual etymologies, see the words : [[в]] [[Тулу]] [[со]] [[своим]] [[самоваром]].  The phrase derives from the fact that [[w:Tula|Tula]] is well-known for [[samovar]].    The phrase was coined by [[w:Chekhov|Chekhov]].

<!-- ===Pronunciation=== -->

===Idiom===
'''в Тулу со своим самоваром'''
# do something that is not needed (''literally:'' to [go to] [[w:Tula|Tula]] with [[samovar]]); see [[owls to Athens]] and [[coals to Newcastle]]
#*''И коллеги удивленно пожимают плечами: В Тулу со своим самоваром?'' [http://www.intertravel.ru/sovet/sovet24.php]
#**''And the colleagues shrug their shoulders: to Tula with the samovar?''

